      <title>瑞士法院判处冈比亚部长反人类罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/swiss-court-convicts-gambian-minister-of-crimes-against-humanity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，瑞士一家法院判定冈比亚前部长在前总统叶海亚·贾梅 (Yahya Jammeh) 政权下犯有危害人类罪，并判处他 20 年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/swiss-court-convicts-gambian-minister-of-crimes-against-humanity</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:25:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称，今年通过达里恩的儿童移民差距增加了 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/child-migration-through-darien-gap-up-40-this-year-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国机构周三报告称，今年迄今为止，通过达里恩差距的儿童移民数量增加了 40%，并将连续第五年创下纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/child-migration-through-darien-gap-up-40-this-year-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
